 \"from\": 209, \"to\": 266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the junior level\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her first meet at the senior level was the 2024 Winter Cup in February.\\u00c2 Now, the 16-year-old is headed to Paris as part of a historic U.S. Olympic gymnastics team that includes Simone Biles, Suni Lee, Jade Carey and Jordan Chiles, who have won a combined 55 medals at world championships and the Olympics.\\u00c2 It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s an incredible moment for the New Jersey native, but was no sure thing.\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999767123884, \"rank\": 2.3287388803724967e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Suni Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 470, \"end\": 480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}, {\"begin\": 485, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"t