ders\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Skye Blakely, 19; Shilese Jones, 21; and Kayla DiCello, 20\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094all suffered injuries and had to drop out of the competition.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shilese_Jones\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shilese Jones\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shilese_Jones\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shilese_Jones\"}, {\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_DiCello\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kayla DiCello\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_DiCello\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_DiCello\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the days\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"trials\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"Blakely\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"20\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094all suffered injuries\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That opened the door for a lesser-known talent to step up.\\u00c2 Rivera was one of a few gymnasts in the hunt for the final spot and she capitalized on the opportunity on Sunday night.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1060, \"end\": 1066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9999994668029615, \"rank\": 5.331759567731973e-07, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"a lesser-known talent\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"a few gymnasts\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"the hunt\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"the final spot\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday night\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her routine on the uneven bars and balance beam ended up being the difference\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094she scored a 14.300 on bars at a 6.1 difficulty score and a 14.275 on beam at a 6.0 difficulty score on Sunday.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy mentality was that I had nothing to lose, so I just went out there and did my best, gave it my all, most importantly,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Rivera said,per NBC News.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1501, \"end\": 1507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9999994668029615, \"rank\": 5.331759567731973e-07, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her routine\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"the uneven bars\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"balance beam\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"the difference\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094she\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"bars\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6.1 difficulty score\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"beam\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6.0 difficulty score\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy mentality\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"NBC News\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imagine being a junior in high school and competing at the U.S. Olym